The schedule file contained a reference scan for each on-source scan; the \textsc{sdcal} task in \textsc{casa} assumes this format.
Polynomial baseline subtraction can occur at this stage, or a continuum subtraction can be applied after the imaging stage is completed to preserve the continuum emission.
